# 🚀 Auto Price Dashboard (PRO Version)

A modern, responsive dashboard for managing product pricing, stock, and automation — inspired by real marketplace systems like Eldorado.gg.

![Preview](preview.png)

---

## ✨ Features

### 💼 Core Features

* 📦 Add / Edit / Delete Products
* 💰 Dynamic Price Management (No Limit)
* 📊 Real-time Dashboard Stats
* 🔍 Live Search & Filtering
* 🔄 Toggle Active / Pause Offer

### ⚡ Advanced Features

* 📈 Stock Visualization (Chart.js)
* 🔔 Toast Notification System
* 💾 Local Storage Persistence
* 🎨 Modern UI (Dark Mode + Clean Design)
* 📱 Fully Responsive (Mobile Friendly)
* ✨ Smooth Animations & Hover Effects

