## 🧠 Use Case

This project simulates a **marketplace seller dashboard** where users can:

* Manage product listings
* Adjust prices dynamically
* Control stock availability
* Monitor product performance

Perfect for:

* 💼 Portfolio Projects
* 🧑‍💻 Freelance Showcase
* 🚀 SaaS Prototype

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

* HTML5
* CSS3 (Flexbox + Animations)
* JavaScript (Vanilla)
* Chart.js

---

## 📦 Installation

Clone this repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Mufti-code/auto-price-dashboard.git
```

Open project:

```bash
cd auto-price-dashboard
```

Run:

* Open `index.html` in browser
  or
* Use Live Server (VS Code)

